  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5aaa17dab8395eadb3554a1fcf5d30c7.avif?t=1740070165\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.poster.avif?t=1740070165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.webm?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.mp4?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your deck for the ultimate roguelike deckbuilder experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect cards and other loot and use them to defeat your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your deck to your playstyle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan out your moves to outsmart your enemies in this turn-based card battler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.poster.avif?t=1740070165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.webm?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.mp4?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated stages - play a new map each time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new cards to add into your deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your cards in various different ways, such as giving them extra effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different enemies with unique abilities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple stages, each with a random powerful boss at the end</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consumable items that are helpful when you're in a pickle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect relics to become more powerful. Your enemies may also have relics of their own!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events - full of surprises! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom mode, where you can choose among various modifiers to spice up the gameplay or increase the challenge!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overtime mode - 10 tiers of increasingly harder runs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5aaa17dab8395eadb3554a1fcf5d30c7.avif?t=1740070165\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.poster.avif?t=1740070165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.webm?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/889d6eb396a8da519746b1cc9ee974c0.mp4?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your deck for the ultimate roguelike deckbuilder experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect cards and other loot and use them to defeat your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your deck to your playstyle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan out your moves to outsmart your enemies in this turn-based card battler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.poster.avif?t=1740070165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.webm?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892060/extras/5ce81795ed5eb4d83e3fd0427ebd89bd.mp4?t=1740070165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated stages - play a new map each time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new cards to add into your deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your cards in various different ways, such as giving them extra effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different enemies with unique abilities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple stages, each with a random powerful boss at the end</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consumable items that are helpful when you're in a pickle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect relics to become more powerful. Your enemies may also have relics of their own!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events - full of surprises! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom mode, where you can choose among various modifiers to spice up the gameplay or increase the challenge!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overtime mode - 10 tiers of increasingly harder runs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul>",
